<p>I am using JSF2. I would like to write, in a c:when tag, a test using the variable of a primefaces  dataGrid. I have tried with many syntaxes, but it seems that the value of test attribute is always true.</p>  <p>id attribute is an Integer.</p>  <p>Is it possible to do that ?</p>  <pre><code>           &lt;p:dataGrid id="pdatagrid" value="#{group.items}" var="item" &gt;                          &lt;c:choose&gt;                             &lt;c:when test="#{!(item.id eq -1)}"&gt;                                 ...                             &lt;/c:when&gt;                             &lt;c:otherwise&gt;                                 ...                            &lt;/c:otherwise&gt;                         &lt;/c:choose&gt;             &lt;/p:dataGrid&gt; </code></pre>